                &lt;P&gt; The master factory for all reflective objects, both those in
                  java.lang.reflect (Fields, Methods, Constructors) as well as their
                  delegates (FieldAccessors, MethodAccessors, ConstructorAccessors).
                  &lt;/P&gt;
